__SqlaTable__.sql:
SELECT categoryId, categoryCode, COUNT(productId) as purchase_count
FROM clickstream
WHERE categoryCode IS NOT NULL AND eventType = 'purchase'
AND __time BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2020-01-01'
GROUP BY categoryId, categoryCode
ORDER BY purchase_count desc
